{"tid":1204634,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"【日行好小事 人便有福了】街頭M巾大派發行動","createTime":"2019-06-11T15:41:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-12T00:03:15.000Z","uid":253129,"like":107,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"ccbb629db74ee036149562aa857123e61be01e46","tid":1204634,"uid":253129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T15:41:09.000Z","msg":"話說今日小妹喺條街度突然黎M<br />\n好彩喺我手足無措既時候有個姨姨遞左塊M巾比我<br />\n如果冇左佢我都唔知點算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n為左答謝呢位無名英雄<br />\n我決定由宜家開始一出街就<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">成個背囊裝滿哂M巾</span></span><br />\n派比有需要人士，希望大家都可以同我一齊做下好事啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大家亦唔需要覺得尷尬<br />\n因為<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">點會有人無端端開你背囊喎</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b75d27d9efec5df26bc15e22241f3fd2470ad04","tid":1204634,"uid":253129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T15:47:19.000Z","msg":"自己推下先 絲打們我地一齊做下善事啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cab4c85c822b348090d7ec4f355868691d09b533","tid":1204634,"uid":253129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T15:50:24.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9357e54059d5f00d90e513e262c171267f84afef","tid":1204634,"uid":205231,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T15:52:35.000Z","msg":"多謝絲打 我都叫個妹咁做先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1acb6311ce0229e68598029e5e6361ecd7c9dafa","tid":1204634,"uid":253129,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T15:56:27.000Z","msg":"有人響應好感動